            <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-columbia-blue mt-0.5">▸</span>
              <span><strong class="text-stone-700">零售银行：</strong>服务个人客户，理财、信贷</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-columbia-blue mt-0.5">▸</span>
              <span><strong class="text-stone-700">金融市场/资管：</strong>银行自营投资、同业业务，偏买方性质</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-columbia-blue mt-0.5">▸</span>
              <span><strong class="text-stone-700">风险合规：</strong>信用评估、内控合规，稳定但晋升慢</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-3 text-sm">真实情况</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-xs text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
